{"tid":1269852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非仍然有得贏","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:51:28.000Z","uid":44646,"like":10,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"34fe770fac1aa8bd3ed5f37adefebeec1ab93e7b","tid":1269852,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"我唔知點解到今日仲有革命浪漫主義主張武力升級<br />\n所有事實都證明我地用武，係以己之短攻敵之長<br />\n<br />\n我地要贏，要持續和理非<br />\n(唔排除局部勇武，例如圍堵敵根據地)<br />\n<br />\n具體而言：<br />\nSTEP 1.<br />\n支持並推動美國國會修例，針對香港違反人權官員、黑警<br />\n(可以加埋台灣)<br />\n送香港牌俾美國打<br />\n甚至可能在法案中迫使香港指定時間前直選<br />\n(中共未必跪，但可望令美國升級針對香港狗官)<br />\n<br />\nSTEP 2.<br />\n區會我地要贏，鼓勵素人參選(已經有人做緊)、投票<br />\n只要唔好ON99界票、焦土<br />\n我地係可能贏返18區(代表一個立會功能組別席位)<br />\n也可減少政府用區會支持來打飛機<br />\n<br />\n以上都比你去勇武有更大殺傷力"},{"pid":"fd310eaa49b1aef20588163409a3ac0745bcf6e3","tid":1269852,"uid":104500,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"各有各做"},{"pid":"d062d6c2d67eea2d5307d9047094fad88bcc8677","tid":1269852,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259aa71ca63f3e20e673e3127259a86d3406e897","tid":1269852,"uid":202137,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"和理非左廿幾年都未夠？"},{"pid":"b479ff2ad984dda57ed4ec38f9e7d55dd4e76fc3","tid":1269852,"uid":248540,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"得啦 縮返埋入你老母個閪繼續和理非啦"},{"pid":"abdcae5fa87ef9e42cc33a2235eddaa2d72240d5","tid":1269852,"uid":76745,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"2014年講都會buy你 而家2019年喇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615142ea2e2371d0d2d989794e475abbe85efff3","tid